NODEJS :>)

?What is NODEJS?

-> NodeJS is a Server Environment. It internally uses javascript to run it. javascript is used to 
run our file.
-> We can connect with database,api and ect...,
-> NodeJS uses V8 engine to execute the code.
-> Mainly used for connect database like WebAPI & MobileAPI.
-> NodeJS runs on the Server Side and Javascript runs on the browser. 